Dia. 01 Helping White
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is supporting White's mistake.
\par
\par After White plays at 2 to destroy the eye, Black can't live anymore.
\par
\par After Black 3, White kills with 4. If Black plays at 4 instead of 3, Black is captured again with White 3. In other words, 3 and 4 are \cf1\b miai\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par }
