Dia. 02 Double Shortage of Liberties
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's hane at 1 is a powerful move, however unfortunately it doesn't work in this situation.
\par
\par White 1 is a good attack. After Black 3, White cuts with 4 and Black can't play from both sides. It is a double shortage of liberties.
\par
\par
\par }
