Dia. 03 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's attachment at 1 is the vital point for living. It is also the 1-2 point.
\par
\par Next, 2 and 3 are miai.
\par
\par In a problem when you try to live, the move which can capture you in many cases, can be the vital point for you too.
\par
\par It is same, when you try to capture something in a problem.
\par }
